public class GCPService

The GCPService background system service acts like a router, forwarding and translating messages between online nodes and Mobile Apps. It sends and receives GCP protocol messages over Socket.io/TCP/IP and translates them to GCP protocol over Android Binder IPC messages.

Mobile Apps can use the messaging API directly by starting and binding to the service or use the convenience client implementation Lounge.
